text: {'text': 'BEST Guinness and cocktails in town!\nThe best way to attack naga house for the most wonderful evening is to grab a couple of friends, order some Guinness and try their unique cocktails that are super affordable! Plenty of delicious food to pick from. After a couple round of drinks, ask the friendly tatted bartenders for off menu special or yummy cocktails like the Ramos Gin fizz, espresso martini twist!', 'languageCode': 'en'}
